## Project Overview

This is a single-file Python Dash dashboard (`theta_dashboard_v4_modern.py`)
that serves two purposes:
1. **Theta Options Terminal** — live options data visualization (charts, tables,
   heatmaps, Greek surfaces) fed by CSV files from a Theta Data API fetcher.
2. **AI Multi-Agent Analyst** — a 7-agent pipeline that calls 3 different LLM
   APIs (Perplexity, xAI, OpenRouter) to predict SPX intraday direction using
   the same CSV data plus live web search.

The dashboard runs on **port 8050** via `app.run(debug=True, host='0.0.0.0', port=8050)`.
It is deployed on **RunPod** (remote GPU cloud, Linux environment).

